is extremely small.

I updated the license creation year information, which had not been
updated for many years.

Bump base and CI for GHC 9.6

- compiles and tests fine with GHC 9.6.1
- CI needs to be regenerated as ubuntu-18.04 isn't supported any longer
- restrict CI runs to branches master and ci-* to avoid duplicate runs

Extend Haskell-CI to GHC 7.x, but without running the testsuite

See #16: `cabal v2-test` does not work out of the box.

CI on GitHub Actions using haskell-ci

Delete a badge of Travis CI

I leave Travis CI.
